============
Installation
============

* Add ``'cosinnus_event', 'appconf', 'bootstrap3', 'easy-thumbnails', 'geoposition', * 'south', 'taggit'`` to ``INSTALLED_APPS``
* Add a setting for the thumbnailer, e.g.
```python
THUMBNAIL_PROCESSORS = (
 'easy_thumbnails.processors.colorspace',
 'easy_thumbnails.processors.autocrop',
 'easy_thumbnails.processors.scale_and_crop',
 'easy_thumbnails.processors.filters',
)
```
See https://github.com/SmileyChris/easy-thumbnails for more details .
* Optionally set a format for the date picker (Javascript-compatible!) by
setting ``COSINNUS_DATETIME_PICK_FORMAT`` globally or
``COSINNUS_EVENT_DATETIME_PICK_FORMAT`` just for this app.
